data.description: Located in the Elmhurst neighborhood, this spectacular ranch home is just a short walk to Providence College and nearby restaurants, coffee shops, and parks. This home offers 3 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom upstairs with a newly renovated in-law apartment downstairs for an increased living area. Head inside to find the open concept living space, flowing seamlessly from the fireplaced living room to the dining area to the kitchen complete with stainless appliances and a great center island. An additional living room, three bedrooms, and the first full bathroom round out the primary level of the home.     Even more awaits you on the basement level with an in-law apartment already established with a living room, full kitchen, full bathroom, bedroom, and laundry room/storage area, plus a backyard walkout with a separate patio area.    This home is situated on a large 11,000+sf lot with a phenomenal deck for summer entertaining and grilling, plus off-street parking for 5 cars. This home would make a great family residence, or capitalize on the additional living space and rent to college students for guaranteed income. You won't want to miss this one!
